narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: Firm introduction to the basics of military communication and behavior. We did interesting case studies which helped us cadets understand some of the real-world impacts our jobs could have in the Air Force and the world.
I learned valuable information for my future Air Force career.
This course taught me a lot of the fundamentals of the USAF. I also was able to practice my presentation skills.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: Interesting case study readings that we got good class discussion from. Class could include more peer to peer interaction through discussing material to increase class cohesion.
The course was very good. I do not see much room for improvement.
The course was great as it was.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: Yes it is a good and interesting class and taught by someone who brings an experienced perspective.
